'''PZM''' is an acronym for Pressure Zone Microphone; it can also be used to describe a boundary [[microphone]] in which the mic capsule faces the boundary a few thousandths of an inch away. PZM is a trademark of [[Crown International]]. 

The PZM can be used as a piano mic.

